        "eligibilityDescription_md": "\n1. The applicant should be a permanent resident of Haryana.\n1. The applicant should possess a valid Parivar Pehchan Patra (PPP).\n1. The applicant should belong to the Scheduled Caste (SC) category.\n1. The applicant should be at least 18 years old.\n1. The applicant should present a GST-paid bill for the purchase of fishing nets.\n1. The applicant can apply only once in two years for this subsidy.\n\n",
